the slaging Pit had to make males so damn heavy!
She sighes and takes the hand which he offered to her, standing up and 
brushing herself off.
Desmonus stretched herself arounf a bit to make sure there was no dust in 
the back, saticfied that there wasn't she then looked towards the men, 
stretching a bit.
Her muscles cramping due to her hunger.


But Desmonus simply waves her hand at Bloodystrikes apology( so I'm lousy at 
spelling, sue me.), trying to keep her temper uncer control and making a 
point not to bring up that he had stepped on her wing...which ached.
But she could stand it.
However, she was going to put a little glitch in the two mens plans for her. 
Clasping her hands in front of her and straightening her back.*

" Hmm...seems like we've landed, and that means that the other half of the 
ship should be connected now. How about that drink?"
